## What Each File Does

| File | Does What |
|------|-----------|
| **main.tf** | Tells Terraform "use AWS" and sets up the AWS connection |
| **vpc.tf** | Creates the network and 6 neighborhoods (subnets) |
| **nat.tf** | Creates 2 exit gates (NAT Gateways) for private servers |
| **routing.tf** | Creates signs that tell traffic where to go |
| **security_groups.tf** | Creates 4 bouncers that decide who can talk to who |
| **flow_logs.tf** | Sets up security cameras to record traffic |
| **variables.tf** | Says "these are the settings you can change" |
| **outputs.tf** | Says "print out these IDs at the end" |
| **terraform.tfvars** | Your actual settings (e.g., "2 availability zones") |

