## How to Use This

### Prerequisites
- AWS account (Workload Account)
- Terraform installed
- AWS CLI configured

### Quick Start

```bash
# 1. Clone or download this code
cd vpc-infrastructure-as-code/terraform

# 2. Initialize Terraform
terraform init

# 3. See what will be created
terraform plan

# 4. Build it
terraform apply

# 5. View what was created
terraform output
```

### What You Get
- VPC ID
- 6 Subnet IDs
- 2 NAT Gateway IPs
- 4 Security Group IDs
- Internet Gateway ID
- CloudWatch log group for logs

### Clean Up (Delete Everything)

```bash
terraform destroy
```

