## Troubleshooting

| Problem | Solution |
|---------|----------|
| "terraform not found" | Install Terraform: `brew install terraform` |
| "credentials not configured" | Run `aws configure --profile workload-account` |
| "quota exceeded" | Check NAT Gateway quota in your region |
| "VPC already exists" | Run `terraform destroy` first |

